<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/1102.html" title="Lost Civil Liberties"> Lost Civil Liberties</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>My mom visited us just before the holiday and brought us an Alice in Wonderland mug that had a disappearing Cheshire cat when you put in hot water. The mug is great (it doesn&#8217;t hurt that I love the Sir John Tenniel&#8217;s illustrations).</p>

	<p>Today I stumbled upon another product from the Unemployed Philosphers Guild: the <a title="Unemployed Philosophers Guild: Lost Civil Liberties mug" href="http://www.philosophersguild.com/index.lasso?page_mode=Product_Detail&#38;item=0236">Lost Civil Liberties mug</a>.</p>

	<p>Amazing how a cup of coffee can share such truths.</p>



 
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="smallcat">Posted in <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?c=Politics">Politics</a></div>
<div class="smalluser"> by <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?author=E.G.+Yarnetsky">E.G. Yarnetsky</a></div>
